"8  Granny Smith apples, peeled and cut into wedges","2 cups sugar","1  (3-ounce) package cream cheese","1/3 cup butter or margarine, cut up","2 1/2 cups self-rising flour","1 cup milk","1/4 cup butter or margarine","1/3 cup cider vinegar","1 teaspoon grated lemon rind","1 teaspoon ground cinnamon","1 teaspoon ground allspice","1/4 teaspoon ground cloves","  Vanilla ice cream (optional)"